{"word":"G1107 - γνωρίζω - gnōrízō - gno-rid'-zo - Certify","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γνωρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">gnōrízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">gno-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Certify</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அறிவி, தெரிவி, விளக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to make known, to know"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko/1097\">G1097</a>; to <i>make known</i>; subjectively to <i>know:</i> - certify, declare, make known, give to understand, do to wit, wot.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1097/1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1106/1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107/1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108/1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110/1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176/176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921/1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922/1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607/2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267/4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268/4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774/4774\">G4774</a>"}]}